imdb.plot outline: It's a Family Affair and you're invited. Keeping God First, Hilarious, Fun-loving, Trendsetters, and an authentic definition of the word "family," Life With the Rankins, is the new web series that YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS!!. Written from the perspective of Wife, Mother, and Blessed Creative Powerhouse, Brandy "BrandyWine" Rankins, watch this family stand in Faith through life's most challenging trials, encourage others, and support their children in the industry of professional acting. A brand new episode will be uploaded on Youtube.com every week and you DON'T WANT TO MISS IT!!. Log onto Youtube right now and "SUBSCRIBE" to this life-changing web series "LIFE WITH THE RANKINS" and get all the official updates. #LifeWiththeRankins #RankinsNation.
